  {
    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Thanks @bobylito for this solution!\r\n\r\nIt's not ideal as it triggers a search every time the page loads, even if the user is not searching (I'm trying to limit the number of requests to Algolia to stay in our quota).\r\nIn my case, the items on the page are already rendered server-side, so I have a kind of blink during the time of the request (you notice it even if it's only a few dozen ms).\r\n\r\nDo you see another option?",
